{"type": "article", "id": 16685, "title": "护肤品包装设计", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-28T06:14:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 69, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135541qK4rJA1QYCIWRNZz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t俄罗斯的设计师 Neretin Stas 做了这些护肤品的包装设计，用了接近皮肤的肉色和有凹凸的外壳，让人不由自主地拿起来。而当触碰到它们时，接触部位又会变红，就像是敏感的皮肤。设计者在包装外面使用了遇热变色的涂漆，让这些护肤品有了高兴或者羞怯的情绪，这种细微的互动也能让人们更加重视自己皮肤健康。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143955bGrvifhZ21oDTJyO.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"578\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261439568st9ykvUBLEaOTdI.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"578\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143956hnrwbWDOBx5L3Xol.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"609\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74449878\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261439577IxvUdFgc6qiukCZ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"578\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143957wNKyVIvurimCeaT8.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"913\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.11613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}